Package: marathonR
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to the 'marathon' Library
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2018-03-18
Maintainer: Hjalmar Boulouednine <hjalmar@b-nine.de>
Author: Steffen Rechner, Hjalmar Boulouednine
Description: This packages provides methods for the uniform sampling of binary matrices with restricted row and column sums.
  For this purpose, the package provides two functions for the uniform sampling of 
    a) binary matrices with prescribed row and column sums.
    b) binary matrices whose row and column sums are restricted by lower and upper bounds.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: methods, Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp, BH
SystemRequirements: gmp
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
